# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CRITICAL: Stray root-level Python backend dirs that live in this repo for
# historical reasons — NOT part of the Next.js frontend. A root /app directory
# SHADOWS src/app for Next.js App Router detection (Next.js prefers <root>/app
# over <root>/src/app when both exist), which SILENTLY BUILDS ZERO ROUTES if
# this directory is present. The build exits with code 0 — no error, all 404s.
#
# This was a production incident on 2026-07-19 affecting telemon.online.
# DO NOT remove these entries without adding a pre-build check.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
/app
/backend
# Nested backend git repo — only present in some local checkouts (on the VPS it's a
# sibling directory outside this build context entirely). Irrelevant to the Next.js
# build either way.
/telegram-dashboard-backend
.env*
!.env.example
npm-debug.log*
test-results
playwright-report
e2e
data/
sessions/
*.db
*.session
.backup
*.log
